WEBVTT

00:00:00.709 --> 00:00:02.319
Gde se ukrštaju

00:00:02.319 --> 00:00:06.636
tehnologija, umetnost i nauka?

00:00:06.636 --> 00:00:08.733
U radoznalosti i čudu,

00:00:08.733 --> 00:00:11.646
jer to nas pokreće da istražujemo,

00:00:11.646 --> 00:00:15.110
jer smo okruženi stvarima
koje ne možemo da vidimo.

00:00:15.110 --> 00:00:16.724
Volim da koristim film

00:00:16.724 --> 00:00:18.260
da bih nas poveo na putovanje

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:20.940
kroz kapije vremena i prostora,

00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:23.314
da bih nevidljivo učinio vidljivim,

00:00:23.314 --> 00:00:24.964
jer to proširuje

00:00:24.964 --> 00:00:26.887
naše horizonte,

00:00:26.887 --> 00:00:29.348
transformiše naše opažanje,

00:00:29.348 --> 00:00:31.678
otvara naše umove